{
  "stem": "9898.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was students in the rabbinical school in black hat, black coats, white socks, you know, and, and those shoes-- black shoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And behind them, a few SS men with machine guns-- hand-machine guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said to the nurse, please, stay here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wait for me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I want to see what they're going to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They run, then, probably another hundred yards-- put them all over-- all at the wall-- there was a wall of a building-- in one line, and machine-gunned them right down, all of them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, this was a little too much for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was close to a nervous breakdown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went to the president of Society Ganz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said, I can't do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I am resigning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was three weeks-- this was in August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went back to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was working on the obstetrics.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was working by myself at nights only.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "With me was an old Jewish midwife, 75 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was a young man at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we're doing mostly deliveries, and mostly peculiar, during the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I could do in one night 12 deliveries-- deliver 12 babies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now we were trained to do everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Today, if there is any complication, they do right away a Cesarean section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "At that time, I was doing breaches, turning around, everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But, one thing interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't give us any gloves, rubber gloves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we didn't have any soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were giving us pieces of soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was like stone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I couldn't clean my hands with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what was I doing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just, under the water, washed the arms, the forearms, the hands from the blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
